{"data":{"allContentfulBlogPost":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"c166JR8T91o2Cyu6kOuCOye","title":"Tech Stack for sherpafeet.com","tags":["FULLSTACK"],"description":{"id":"c166JR8T91o2Cyu6kOuCOyedescriptionTextNode","description":"The technology stack which powers sherpafeet.com, a platform for trekking guides in the Indian Himalayas."},"createdAt":"2017-12-29T01:56:55.983Z","blog":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p><a href=\"https://sherpafeet.com\">sherpafeet</a> is a platform for trekking guides. Trekking guides is a disorganised industry.\nAnyone who has done a couple of treks can claim to be a trek guide. Thats great. But in the process, the native people who depend on this profession for their livelihood were losing out. sherpafeet is a social enterprise which not only helps the native people but is grounded on the core concepts of sustainability.</p>\n<h2 id=\"technology-which-drives-sherpafeet\"><a href=\"#technology-which-drives-sherpafeet\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Technology which drives sherpafeet</h2>\n<p>The sherpafeet platform is built on the MERN Stack. That is</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mongodb.com/\">Mongodb</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://reactjs.org\">reactjs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://expressjs.com\">Express</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org\">Nodejs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"hosting-and-devops\"><a href=\"#hosting-and-devops\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hosting and Devops</h2>\n<p>The platform is hosted on Amazon Web Services.</p>\n<h2 id=\"search-functionality\"><a href=\"#search-functionality\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Search Functionality</h2>\n<p>The search functionality on sherpafeet is powered by <a href=\"https://www.elastic.co/\">Elastic Search</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"apis\"><a href=\"#apis\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>APIs</h2>\n<p>Instead of the traditional REST APIs we use <a href=\"http://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"//images.contentful.com/ojam5vx77jn8/r42cQMeDdIIGwYuw6qay4/81f74976b37358a175fb6a5ec281446d/bg.jpg\" alt=\"Featured Image of test blog\"></p>","timeToRead":1}},"featuredImage":{"title":"sherpafeet Logo ","resize":{"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/580cvEs88gYyGiqymo4MGM/ee5b9f2f751be0df15d2a95f374de572/sflogo.png?w=1200&h=630&fl=progressive&q=50&fit=fill&f=faces"},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.281602002503129,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/580cvEs88gYyGiqymo4MGM/ee5b9f2f751be0df15d2a95f374de572/sflogo.png?w=800&q=50","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/580cvEs88gYyGiqymo4MGM/ee5b9f2f751be0df15d2a95f374de572/sflogo.png?w=200&h=156&q=50 200w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/580cvEs88gYyGiqymo4MGM/ee5b9f2f751be0df15d2a95f374de572/sflogo.png?w=400&h=312&q=50 400w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/580cvEs88gYyGiqymo4MGM/ee5b9f2f751be0df15d2a95f374de572/sflogo.png?w=800&h=624&q=50 800w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/580cvEs88gYyGiqymo4MGM/ee5b9f2f751be0df15d2a95f374de572/sflogo.png?w=1024&h=799&q=50 1024w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}},"author":{"name":"Jai","authorBio":"Jai is passionate about social issues and causes. He is the founder of sherpafeet and Tech47.","profilePicture":{"title":"Jai Profile Picture","resolutions":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":125,"height":125,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/48JEu6lPigqI46gmeyuysC/4bbc705827749cebe670959385fb7cc2/jai.jpeg?w=125&q=50","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/48JEu6lPigqI46gmeyuysC/4bbc705827749cebe670959385fb7cc2/jai.jpeg?w=125&h=125&q=50 1x,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/48JEu6lPigqI46gmeyuysC/4bbc705827749cebe670959385fb7cc2/jai.jpeg?w=188&h=188&q=50 1.5x,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/48JEu6lPigqI46gmeyuysC/4bbc705827749cebe670959385fb7cc2/jai.jpeg?w=250&h=250&q=50 2x,\n//images.ctfassets.net/ojam5vx77jn8/48JEu6lPigqI46gmeyuysC/4bbc705827749cebe670959385fb7cc2/jai.jpeg?w=375&h=375&q=50 3x"}}}}}]}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/blog/sherpafeet","prev":{"id":"c6wo4Wf9gbe6cK2Q66oo2MY","featured":null,"title":"Templating Technology","tags":["SERVERLESS"],